00607         ParticleSettings *part = (ParticleSettings*)ptr->id.data;
00608         
00609         if (part->effector_weights == ew)
00610             return BLI_sprintfN("effector_weights");
00611     }
00612     else {
00613         Object *ob = (Object*)ptr->id.data;
00614         ModifierData *md;
00615         
00616         /* check softbody modifier */
00617         md = (ModifierData *)modifiers_findByType(ob, eModifierType_Softbody);
00618         if (md) {
00619             /* no pointer from modifier data to actual softbody storage, would be good to add */
00620             if (ob->soft->effector_weights == ew)
00621                 return BLI_sprintfN("modifiers[\"%s\"].settings.effector_weights", md->name);
00622         }
00623         
00624         /* check cloth modifier */
00625         md = (ModifierData *)modifiers_findByType(ob, eModifierType_Cloth);
00626         if (md) {
00627             ClothModifierData *cmd = (ClothModifierData *)md;
00628             
00629             if (cmd->sim_parms->effector_weights == ew)
00630                 return BLI_sprintfN("modifiers[\"%s\"].settings.effector_weights", md->name);
00631         }
00632         
00633         /* check smoke modifier */
00634         md = (ModifierData *)modifiers_findByType(ob, eModifierType_Smoke);
00635         if (md) {
00636             SmokeModifierData *smd = (SmokeModifierData *)md;
00637             
00638             if (smd->domain->effector_weights == ew)
00639                 return BLI_sprintfN("modifiers[\"%s\"].settings.effector_weights", md->name);
00640         }
00641 
00642         /* check dynamic paint modifier */
00643         md = (ModifierData *)modifiers_findByType(ob, eModifierType_DynamicPaint);
00644         if (md) {
00645             DynamicPaintModifierData *pmd = (DynamicPaintModifierData *)md;
00646 
00647             if (pmd->canvas) {
00648                 DynamicPaintSurface *surface = pmd->canvas->surfaces.first;
00649 
00650                 for (; surface; surface = surface->next) {
00651                     if (surface->effector_weights == ew)
00652                         return BLI_sprintfN("modifiers[\"%s\"].canvas_settings.canvas_surfaces[\"%s\"]"
00653                                             ".effector_weights", md->name, surface->name);
00654                 }
00655             }
00656         }
00657     }
00658     return NULL;
00659 }
